short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Express your opinions for any page!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Missing the dislike count from Youtube? Want to express your love or hate for a website?

Opinion8d is an extension that allows you to like and dislike any website! See what others think of the current site with a live count and change your opinions at any time.

Want more to be more Opinion8d? 
Check out the website: https://opinion8d.me/
